<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="bg">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>AI Бриф · {{ date_human }}</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500;600&family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Spectral:wght@600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --ink: #0b1220;          /* дълбоко мастилено синьо — небе преди отваряне */
    --panel: #111a2e;
    --panel-2: #16203a;
    --line: #233252;
    --text: #d9e1f2;
    --muted: #8593b3;
    --green: #34d399;
    --yellow: #fbbf24;
    --red: #f87171;
    {% if regime == "Offensive" %}--regime: #34d399; --regime-dim: rgba(52,211,153,.12);
    {% elif regime == "Cash" %}--regime: #f87171; --regime-dim: rgba(248,113,113,.12);
    {% else %}--regime: #fbbf24; --regime-dim: rgba(251,191,36,.12);{% endif %}
  }
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    background: var(--ink); color: var(--text);
    font-family: "IBM Plex Sans", sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .mono { font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", monospace; }
  .wrap { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px 60px; }

  /* ── Хедър: режимът Е дизайнът ── */
  header {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--regime-dim), transparent 70%);
    padding: 36px 0 28px;
  }
  .header-inner { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16px; }
  .masthead h1 { font-family: "Spectral", serif; font-size: 26px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .3px; }
  .masthead .date { color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 4px; }
  .regime-badge {
    font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", monospace; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--regime); border: 2px solid var(--regime); border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 10px 22px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
    box-shadow: 0 0 28px var(--regime-dim);
  }
  .regime-reason { color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; text-align: right; max-width: 360px; margin-top: 6px; }

  section { margin-top: 44px; }
  h2 {
    font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", monospace; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2.5px; color: var(--muted);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  h2::before { content: "// "; color: var(--regime); }

  /* ── Термометър ── */
  .thermo { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr)); gap: 12px; }
  .t-card {
    background: var(--panel); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 14px 16px; border-top: 3px solid var(--line);
  }
  .t-card.green { border-top-color: var(--green); }
  .t-card.yellow { border-top-color: var(--yellow); }
  .t-card.red { border-top-color: var(--red); }
  .t-name { font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: var(--muted); }
  .t-val { font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", monospace; font-size: 21px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 6px; }
  .t-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 4px; }

  .prose { background: var(--panel); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-left: 3px solid var(--regime);
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px 24px; font-size: 15.5px; }

  /* ── Сектори ── */
  .sectors { display: grid; gap: 12px; }
  .sector-row { background: var(--panel); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 16px 20px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 150px 1fr; gap: 16px; align-items: start; }
  .sector-name { font-weight: 600; }
  .sector-etf { font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", monospace; font-size: 12px; color: var(--regime); }
  .sector-chain { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text); }
  .sector-meta { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 4px; }

  /* ── Action карти ── */
  .stock-card { background: var(--panel); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 22px; overflow: hidden; }
  .stock-head { padding: 18px 24px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px;
    background: var(--panel-2); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .ticker { font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", monospace; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--regime); }
  .company { color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; margin-left: 10px; }
  .price-tag { font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", monospace; font-size: 18px; }
  .stock-body { padding: 20px 24px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr; gap: 24px; }
  @media (max-width: 760px) { .stock-body, .sector-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .block h3 { font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    color: var(--muted); margin: 14px 0 6px; }
  .block h3:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .kv { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: 2px 14px;
    font-size: 13.5px; padding: 3px 0; border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--line); }
  .kv b { font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", monospace; font-weight: 500; text-align: right; }
  .why { font-size: 14.5px; }
  ul.tight { padding-left: 18px; font-size: 13.5px; }
  ul.tight li { margin: 4px 0; }
  .plan { background: var(--regime-dim); border: 1px solid var(--regime);
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px 16px; margin-top: 12px; }
  .plan .kv { border-bottom-color: rgba(255,255,255,.08); }
  .warn { color: var(--yellow); font-size: 13px; }

  /* ── Watchlist ── */
  .watch-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 14px; }
  .watch-card { background: var(--panel); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px 18px; }
  .watch-card .ticker { font-size: 17px; color: var(--yellow); }
  .watch-card p { font-size: 13px; margin-top: 8px; color: var(--text); }
  .watch-trigger { font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 8px;
    border-top: 1px dotted var(--line); padding-top: 8px; }

  footer { margin-top: 60px; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); padding-top: 20px;
    font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
    .regime-badge { animation: pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite; }
    @keyframes pulse { 50% { box-shadow: 0 0 44px var(--regime-dim); } }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="header-inner">
    <div class="masthead">
      <h1>Персонален AI Инвестиционен Бриф</h1>
      <div class="date mono">{{ date_human }} · генериран {{ generated_at }} CET · 90 мин преди US pre-market</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="regime-badge">{{ regime }}</div>
      <div class="regime-reason">{{ regime_reason }}</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="wrap">

<section>
  <h2>Пазарен термометър</h2>
  <div class="thermo">
    {% for ind in thermometer.indicators %}
    <div class="t-card {{ ind.status }}">
      <div class="t-name">{{ ind.name }}</div>
      <div class="t-val">{{ ind.value if ind.value is not none else "—" }}</div>
      <div class="t-label">{{ ind.label }}</div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Макро бриф</h2>
  <div class="prose">{{ macro_brief }}
  {% if regime_comment %}<br><br><span style="color:var(--muted)">{{ regime_comment }}</span>{% endif %}
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Секторна карта · следващите 2–6 седмици</h2>
  <div class="sectors">
    {% for s in sector_logic %}
    <div class="sector-row">
      <div>
        <div class="sector-name">{{ s.sector }}</div>
        <div class="sector-etf">{{ s.etf }}</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="sector-chain">{{ s.chain }}</div>
        <div class="sector-meta">Хоризонт: {{ s.horizon_weeks }} седмици</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Action · {{ action|length }} тикъра</h2>
  {% for st in action %}
  {% set p = st.plan %}
  <div class="stock-card">
    <div class="stock-head">
      <div><span class="ticker">{{ st.ticker }}</span><span class="company">{{ st.company }} · {{ st.sector }}</span></div>
      <div class="price-tag">${{ st.price }} <span style="color:var(--muted);font-size:13px">pivot ${{ st.pivot }} ({{ st.pct_from_pivot }}%)</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="stock-body">
      <div class="block">
        <h3>Защо точно сега</h3>
        <div class="why">{{ st.ai.why_now }}</div>
        <h3>Бизнес</h3>
        <div class="why">{{ st.ai.business_bg }}</div>
        <h3>Катализатори · 4–8 седмици</h3>
        <ul class="tight">{% for c in st.ai.catalysts %}<li>{{ c }}</li>{% endfor %}</ul>
        <h3>Рискове</h3>
        <ul class="tight">{% for r in st.ai.risks %}<li>{{ r }}</li>{% endfor %}</ul>
        {% if st.ai.warning %}<p class="warn">⚠ {{ st.ai.warning }}</p>{% endif %}
        <h3>Short Interest</h3>
        <div class="why" style="font-size:13.5px">{{ st.short_view.interpretation }}</div>
        <h3>Опции</h3>
        <div class="kv"><span>IV / IVR</span><b>{{ st.options.iv or "—" }}% / {{ st.options.iv_rank or "—" }}{% if st.options.iv_rank_quality %} ({{ st.options.iv_rank_quality }}){% endif %}</b></div>
        <div class="kv"><span>P/C ratio</span><b>{{ st.options.put_call_ratio or "—" }}</b></div>
        <div class="kv"><span>Стратегия</span><b>{{ st.options.strategy }}</b></div>
        <div class="why" style="font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:6px">{{ st.options.strategy_reason }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="block">
        <h3>Техническа картина</h3>
        <div class="kv"><span>Формация</span><b>{{ st.base_type }} ({{ st.base_depth_pct }}%)</b></div>
        <div class="kv"><span>Weinstein Stage</span><b>{{ st.weinstein_stage }}</b></div>
        <div class="kv"><span>RS Line</span><b>{{ "нов максимум" if st.rs_status == "new_high" else "близо до максимум" }}</b></div>
        <div class="kv"><span>50DMA / 200DMA</span><b>${{ st.ma50 }} / ${{ st.ma200 }}</b></div>
        <div class="kv"><span>Обем (vs 50d avg)</span><b>{{ st.volume_ratio }}x{{ " ✓ пробивен" if st.breakout_volume else "" }}</b></div>
        <h3>Фундамент</h3>
        <div class="kv"><span>EPS ръст YoY</span><b>{{ st.eps_growth_yoy }}%</b></div>
        <div class="kv"><span>Revenue ръст YoY</span><b>{{ st.revenue_growth_yoy }}%</b></div>
        <div class="kv"><span>ROE</span><b>{{ st.roe }}%</b></div>
        <div class="kv"><span>P/E / Fwd P/E</span><b>{{ st.pe|round(1) if st.pe else "—" }} / {{ st.forward_pe|round(1) if st.forward_pe else "—" }}</b></div>
        <div class="kv"><span>Inst. ownership</span><b>{{ st.inst_ownership_pct }}%</b></div>
        <h3>Earnings</h3>
        <div class="kv"><span>Следващ отчет</span><b>{{ st.earnings.next_earnings or "—" }}{% if st.earnings.days_to_earnings is not none %} ({{ st.earnings.days_to_earnings }}д){% endif %}</b></div>
        <div class="kv"><span>Препоръка</span><b>{{ st.ai.earnings_call }}</b></div>
        <div class="plan">
          <h3 style="color:var(--regime)">План · риск ${{ p.max_risk_usd|int }}{% if p.sizing_factor < 1 %} (Defensive ×{{ p.sizing_factor }}){% endif %}</h3>
          <div class="kv"><span>Entry</span><b>${{ p.entry_range[0] }} – ${{ p.entry_range[1] }}</b></div>
          <div class="kv"><span>Stop ({{ p.stop_basis }})</span><b>${{ p.stop_loss }}</b></div>
          <div class="kv"><span>Брой акции</span><b>{{ p.shares }}</b></div>
          <div class="kv"><span>Инвестиция</span><b>${{ "{:,.0f}".format(p.total_investment) }} ({{ p.pct_of_portfolio }}%)</b></div>
          <div class="kv"><span>Цел 1 (2:1)</span><b>${{ p.target_1 }}</b></div>
          <div class="kv"><span>Цел 2</span><b style="font-size:11.5px">{{ p.target_2 }}</b></div>
          <div class="kv"><span>Хоризонт</span><b>{{ p.time_horizon }}</b></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {% else %}
  <div class="prose">Днес нито един кандидат не покрива всички критерии за Action. Това е информация, не провал — кешът също е позиция.</div>
  {% endfor %}
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Watchlist · {{ watchlist|length }}</h2>
  <div class="watch-grid">
    {% for st in watchlist %}
    <div class="watch-card">
      <span class="ticker">{{ st.ticker }}</span>
      <span class="company">{{ st.company }}</span>
      <p>{{ st.ai.why_now }}</p>
      <div class="watch-trigger"><b>Trigger:</b> {{ st.ai.watchlist_trigger }}
        · зона ${{ (st.pivot * 0.98)|round(2) }}–${{ (st.pivot * 1.02)|round(2) }}</div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  Само за информационни цели. Не представлява финансов съвет, инвестиционна препоръка
  или предложение за покупка/продажба на ценни книжа. Данните идват от публични API-та
  и могат да съдържат грешки или закъснения. Всяко инвестиционно решение е лична отговорност.
  <br>Генерирано автоматично · Персонален AI Инвестиционен Бриф v1.0
</footer>

</div>
</body>
</html>
